QuestData.Title: Vess-Guard Duty
QuestData.Description: Vess-Guard Vik'az co-ordinates the defense forces at Zan'vess. He is worth ten mantid in battle, and his presence inspires the Zan'thik who fight alongside him.$B$BNeedless to say, we need him dead.$B$BHe patrols the housing area at the center of the island.
